<p><b>What are the key differences between ISO 14001 and ISO 50001?</b> ISO 14001 vs. Firstly, ISO 50001 focuses solely on energy consumption, whereas ISO 14001 examines the overall environmental impact. Secondly, even though the requirements for ISO 14001 certification cover energy, they are not as granular as those mandated by the ISO 50001 standard.</p>